synonyms.synonym: Activated Cdc42-associated guanine nucleotide exchange factor

protein.general_function: Involved in guanyl-nucleotide exchange factor activity
protein.specific_function: Guanine nucleotide-exchange factor (GEF) that activates CDC42 by exchanging bound GDP for free GTP

reference.reference_text: Lin Q, Yang W, Baird D, Feng Q, Cerione RA: Identification of a DOCK180-related guanine nucleotide exchange factor that is capable of mediating a positive feedback activation of Cdc42. J Biol Chem. 2006 Nov 17;281(46):35253-62. Epub 2006 Sep 12.
